this tuition freeze will ensure tuition fees of B.C. are among the lowest in Canada . 
in other provinces such as Ontario tuition fees have increased by 20 % in recent years and enrolment has declined . 
even today in British Columbia the government announced that it is removing tuition fees completely for adult basic education . 
